data.description: Welcome home to this stunning property in the heart of the coveted Cane Bay Plantation community! With access to ample recreation, abundant green spaces, miles of walking trails, plentiful shopping/dining options, & quality healthcare facilities, it is no surprise that Cane Bay is considered one of the top master-planned communities in the US. The Coves offers an active, outdoor lifestyle amongst a 300-acre lake system. Take advantage of the natural splendor by launching from the boathouse, or enjoy a relaxing dip in the lakeside pool. This home is the epitome of southern charm with it's double front porches & well manicured landscaping. The main level boasts an open floor plan, perfect for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen is spacious & opens up to the living room, & there is a separateformal dining area. Plentiful storage space throughout! The owner's suite is also on the main level as an added bonus! On the second level you will find an additional 3 bedrooms, one with an en-suite bath, & a large bonus room (5th bedroom) with built-ins, & additional full bath. The backyard is fully fenced-in & has a screened-in porch as well as a spacious additional brick slab, the perfect layout for entertaining or watching the kids or pets play! You do not want to miss this opportunity, schedule a showing TODAY!
